HEADWORD: Inescate
<hw>In*es"cate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>inescatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>inescare</ets>; <ets>in-</ets> in +
